item.title: First baseball game ever at Yankees Stadium, Bronx - Yankees vs. Orioles
item.description: First baseball game ever! Pictures from the Yankees Stadium, Bronx - Yankees vs. Orioles. Unfortunately Orioles lost that game on Saturday. They won the game on Sunday 5-2. <img src="/img/2016/10/img_20161001_164414.jpg?w=1024" alt="img_20161001_164414"> <img src="/img/2016/10/img_20161001_164342.jpg?w=1024" alt="img_20161001_164342"> <img src="/img/2016/10/img_20161001_164327.jpg?w=1024" alt="img_20161001_164327"> <img src="/img/2016/10/img_20161001_163114.jpg?w=1024" alt="img_20161001_163114">
